00:07:03.100 --> 00:07:10.420
Now, I listened to the talk of Shri Mataji in 1984 and, as Mr. Rajesh Shah has told you,

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:17.400
that in the presence of Mother the Kundalini of a person awakens and he gets the experience of a cool breeze.

00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:25.600
