00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:31.740
as many persons initially have, so I very humbly requested Shri Mataji

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:39.400
that, "Mother, I would like to do some research work because I would like to find out whether actually

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:45.280
one gets the feeling of the cool breeze or it is simply a subjective feeling or

