You told me earlier also it might be due to hypnosis or other thing." So I took the permission of Shri Mataji

00:07:54.820 --> 00:08:01.860
into my University faculty meeting and I told them that, "I want to work on sahaja yoga and to establish

00:08:02.060 --> 00:08:08.520
whether one gets the cool breeze or not." There was a little opposition in the faculty meeting

00:08:08.820 --> 00:08:15.820
because they wanted to work more on  fundamental aspects but ultimately seeing that yoga is very important

00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:23.400
and one must know what happens, you see, when yoga is done in the body, the University agreed on it

00:08:23.580 --> 00:08:30.580
