00:11:31.580 --> 00:11:38.120
and that is how the work of Dr. Chugh started, you see and we did the work on patients and we

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:43.300
took two groups, you see, we took the patients of Hypertension as well as Bronchial Asthma.

00:11:43.620 --> 00:11:49.420
