00:11:49.860 --> 00:11:56.640
and, to our surprise, we found it gave a dramatic affect. 98%, if I am correct,

00:11:56.860 --> 00:12:02.780
you see, the patients of hypertension improved and then they were without drugs on follow-up

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:09.160
